BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Frequently Asked Questions) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 676.2 Td (Q: How often should I update this binder?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 660.2 Td (Update after every doctor appointment, medication change, or new diagnosis. Review the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 646.2 Td (entire binder every 6 months to ensure accuracy.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 618.4 Td (Q: Should I bring this to every appointment?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 602.4 Td (Yes! Having your complete medical history, current medications, and questions prepared) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 588.4 Td (makes appointments more efficient and ensures nothing is missed.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 560.6 Td (Q: What if I have multiple conditions?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 544.6 Td (This binder is designed to track everything in one place. You may want to add sections or) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 530.6 Td (extra tracking pages for specific conditions.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 502.8 Td (Q: Should I keep a digital copy?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 486.8 Td (Yes. Take photos of completed pages and store in a secure cloud location. Some prefer a) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 472.8 Td (digital health app alongside this physical binder.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 445.0 Td (Q: What about my children's records?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 429.0 Td (Create a separate binder for each family member. Children especially need immunization and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 415.0 Td (growth records tracked carefully.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 387.2 Td (Q: How do I organize lab results?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 371.2 Td (Keep them chronological. Highlight any values outside normal range. Track trends over time) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 357.2 Td (to discuss with your doctor.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 329.4 Td (Q: What if I change doctors?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 313.4 Td (This binder makes transitions easy. Your new doctor will appreciate having complete) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 299.4 Td (records. Request copies of records from your previous doctor.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 271.6 Td (Q: Is this HIPAA compliant?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 255.6 Td (This is your personal health record. Keep it secure as you would any sensitive document.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 241.6 Td (Do not leave it in public places.) Tj ET
endstream
